steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitparent" and Comment "Table jitparent"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitparent" display
When I add new table with Name "jitchildrene2e" and Comment "Testing jitchildrene2e"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitchildrene2e" display
When I drag the table Name "jitchildrene2e" to new location with x: "500", y: "0"
When I trigger relation popup established from table Name "jitparent" to table Name "jitchildrene2e"
When I check radio button popup Name "has one"
When I press Save button modal popup
Then I should see the realtion path display
When I add new column with Name "jitera" Type "counter_cache" for Table name "jitparent"
Then I should see the number of item in dropdown menu Name "Children Table" is empty
When I close the modal popup
When I open relation popup of pair "jitparent-jitchildrene2e"
When I check radio button popup Name "has many"
When I press Save button modal popup
When I add new column with Name "jitera" Type "counter_cache" for Table name "jitparent"
When I update popup with dropdown Name "Children Table" to value "jitchildrene2es" by clicking
